# FintasTech — Research Lab

> **Open-source educational framework for rule-based multi-agent stock
> research + on-chain paper-trading simulation.**
>
> **FOR EDUCATION AND RESEARCH USE ONLY. NOT INVESTMENT ADVICE.**
> No real orders. No real funds. Mock-only on-chain assets. See
> [`DISCLAIMER.md`](./DISCLAIMER.md).

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](./LICENSE)
[![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-educational-orange.svg)](./DISCLAIMER.md)
