## 🗺️ Repository layout

```
FintasTech/
├── DISCLAIMER.md               # ★ Legal / educational posture
├── README.md
├── pyproject.toml              # Python package metadata
├── requirements.txt
│
├── src/fintastech/             # 🐍 Research backend (FastAPI)
│   ├── agents/                 #   18 analyst modules
│   │   ├── masters.py          #   Buffett, Munger, Graham, Lynch, …
│   │   ├── technical.py        #   RSI / MACD / MA / Bollinger
│   │   ├── fundamental.py      #   P/E, ROE, margin, growth, debt
│   │   ├── valuation.py        #   DCF, earnings yield, relative value
│   │   ├── sentiment.py        #   Momentum & volatility proxy
│   │   └── advisor.py          #   ResearchOrchestrator (blends all)
│   ├── simulation/portfolio.py #   ★ Paper-trading ledger
│   ├── backtesting/engine.py   #   Walk-forward backtest
│   ├── data/yahoo_provider.py  #   Live public market data
│   ├── api/                    #   FastAPI routes
│   └── models/                 #   Pydantic schemas
│
├── blockchain/                 # ⛓ Smart contracts
│   ├── contracts/
│   │   ├── FintasVault.sol             # ★ Paper-trading vault (mock-only)
│   │   ├── FintasSignalRegistry.sol    # ★ Immutable research-signal log
│   │   └── MockUSDC.sol                # Test asset w/ faucet
│   ├── test/                           # 26 tests (happy + edge + reverts)
│   └── scripts/
│       ├── deploy.js                   # allow-listed chains only
│       ├── seed-demo.js
│       ├── e2e-demo.js                 # 6-step end-to-end demo
│       └── oracle-bridge.js            # backend → chain
│
├── frontend/                   # 🎨 Next.js dApp
│   └── src/app/
│       ├── simulation/         # ★ Paper-trading UI
│       ├── vault/              # ★ On-chain vault (MetaMask)
│       ├── analysis/, backtest/
│       └── …
│
└── scripts/
    └── auto_research_loop.py   # ★ One-command automated research
```

