## 🧪 Testing & verification

```bash
# Python
pytest
ruff check .

# Smart contracts
cd blockchain && npm test && npm run coverage

# End-to-end demo (deploy + seed + deposit + oracle tick + withdraw)
npx hardhat run scripts/e2e-demo.js --network localhost

# Frontend type-check
cd frontend && npx tsc --noEmit
```

