## 🎓 Use as an academic / coursework project

FintasTech cleanly maps to common blockchain / fintech coursework rubrics:

| Criterion                    | How this project scores                                                            |
| :--------------------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Innovation & originality** | Multi-agent explainable research signals as an on-chain audit primitive.           |
| **Smart-contract functionality** | ERC20 shares, oracle feed, circuit breaker, guardian, emergency withdraw.     |
| **Code quality & security**  | Roles + ReentrancyGuard + Pausable + custom errors + rate/delta limits + 26 tests. |
| **Interaction & usability**  | Full Next.js dApp + Hardhat scripts + live paper-trading dashboard + e2e demo.     |

See [`COURSE_PROJECT.md`](./COURSE_PROJECT.md) for a ready-to-submit write-up.

